[Amit Varma]: If you enjoyed listening to this episode, then go to sceneunseen.in, the homepage of

00:41:48.320 --> 00:41:49.320
[Amit Varma]: the Scene and the Unseen.

00:41:49.320 --> 00:41:55.720
[Amit Varma]: I have done previous episodes on immigration with Shikha Sodh Dalmia and on protectionism

00:41:55.720 --> 00:41:56.720
[Amit Varma]: with Anupam Manoor.

